1. Write a menu driven C Program to design a simple calculator which solves 10
operations - 4 Arithmetic, 4 Relational and any two of your choice. The program
should loop till the user wishes to stop.
2. Write a C program to accept three numbers from the user. Find the greater two among
the three and pass them as parameters to the user defined functions given below.
a. sumaver ( ... ) which finds the sum and average of the two numbers. Print the
sum and return the average.
b. printeven ( ... ) which prints all the even numbers between the given two
numbers
